entry.content: I like to share this story every national coming out day not to celebrate me coming out but to remind parents its their job to love their kids unconditionally. The greatest gift my parents ever gave me was that of freedom to be myself. I found a partner I love, we raised a daughter, we made a good life for ourselves and their choices that day helped lay the groundwork.
